data.description: Looking for room to roam and privacy?   Look no further than this updated 3 bedroom, 2 full bath home with a wood burning fireplace in the spacious living room.  The kitchen has been updated, and all kitchen appliances stay (range and dishwasher 2024). Two bedrooms and one full bath complete the first floor.  Upstairs is the primary bedroom, a large full bath, and a large second floor laundry.  Outside, 10 acres await you on this partially wooded property with four fenced pastures/paddocks.  48 x 36 barn with water and electricity (built 2008) has three horse stalls with room for at least three more. Upstairs is a huge hayloft/storage area.  Amish built (2020) chicken coop is available as well.  The pond located at the rear of the property is a peaceful retreat for you, family and friends.  Updates include Kinetico water softener (2019), reverse osmosis system (2019), new water pressure tank (2019), septic pump replaced (2024) and has a 3 year warranty, and windows replaced (2015).  The two+ car (24 x 24) garage was built in 2004.
